    "### 2.1 Examining COG Internal Structure\n",
    "\n",
    "Understanding the internal structure of a COG helps optimize data access patterns:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Tile Organization:** How data is spatially organized\n",
    "2. **Overview Hierarchy:** Multiple resolution levels available\n",
    "3. **Compression Settings:** Impact on file size and read performance\n",
    "4. **Block Structure:** Internal data layout for efficient access\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2.2 COG Validation\n",
    "\n",
    "Key characteristics of a valid COG:\n",
    "- Tiled structure with consistent block sizes\n",
    "- Internal overviews at appropriate levels\n",
    "- Proper metadata organization\n",
    "- Compatible compression settings"
